<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11117] [AccessController] checkAndPut/Delete hook should check only Read permission</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11117</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We check for Read and Write permissions in checkAndPut/Delete hooks. Here we check for the condition part alone and so can check for Read permission alone. Later prePut/Delete hook is getting called with Put/Delete mutation and in that we properly check for the Write permission&lt;/p&gt;</description>
